sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant PERM as Permission Service
  participant R as Retrieval Orchestrator
  participant S as Search Indexes
  participant G as Knowledge Graph
  participant P as Playbook Rule Store
  participant E as Evidence Pack Builder
  participant M as Model Gateway
  participant A as Audit Service
  U->>API: AI question
  API->>PERM: tenant/matter/AI policy check
  PERM-->>API: allowed scope
  API->>R: query + scope
  R->>S: keyword/vector search with filters
  R->>G: graph query
  R->>P: rule lookup
  R->>PERM: post-retrieval filter
  R->>E: relevant chunks + graph facts + rules
  E->>M: evidence pack
  M-->>API: grounded answer + citations
  API->>A: AI query/retrieval/response audit
  API-->>U: answer with citations/warnings
